A Gopher client.

Feature :

   - Ability to load other programs with different file formats.
   - Full caching of directories and files.
   - Searching supported.
   - Bookmark support.
   - Directories are searchable by name.
   - Statistics on size of cache, number of files in the cache, and number
     of documents in the queue.
   - Ability to save files and directories.
   - ASK menus.
   - Context menus for individual gopher items.
   - Right click context menus on all items providing all available
     information on a resource.
   - Managerspeak.

WWW: http://opop.nols.com/forg.shtml
